WEBVTT

00:13:30.701 --> 00:13:34.216
And that injunction is without condition,

00:13:34.240 --> 00:13:36.559
and I think that's really
important to emphasize.

00:13:36.583 --> 00:13:41.617
It is without condition; men are to behave
this way according to the Quran,

00:13:41.641 --> 00:13:44.549
regardless of how a woman is dressed.

00:13:45.687 --> 00:13:48.973
And then it turns to women
and says the exact same thing --

00:13:48.997 --> 00:13:51.857
lower your gaze and guard your chastity --

00:13:51.881 --> 00:13:55.930
and then instructs women
to don a head scarf

00:13:55.954 --> 00:13:58.502
or to take the head scarf
that they're already wearing

00:13:58.526 --> 00:14:00.457
and cover the rest of their body.